---
import Container from "../components/Container.astro";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About DigitalSoup">
  <main class="pb-10 pt-36 md:pt-40">
    <Container>
      <section class="section-shell p-8 md:p-12">
        <p class="section-kicker">About us</p>
        <h1 class="mt-4 text-4xl font-bold text-[#0b1220] md:text-5xl">We build growth engines, not random campaigns.</h1>
        <div class="mt-6 grid gap-5 text-[#3b4d75] md:grid-cols-2">
          <p>
            DigitalSoup combines strategic planning, creative execution, and data analysis into one operating rhythm. We focus on channels that can scale and on messaging that actually moves people to act.
          </p>
          <p>
            Our clients work with us because we keep things clear: priorities, numbers, and accountability. Each initiative is tied to pipeline, revenue, or retention.
          </p>
          <p>
            We are intentionally cross-functional. Paid media, SEO, design, and analytics collaborate from day one so your brand experience stays consistent across touchpoints.
          </p>
          <p>
            Whether you are launching a new offer or fixing an underperforming funnel, we help you move faster with fewer assumptions and better decisions.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-8">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Let us plan your next 90 days</a>
        </div>
      </section>
    </Container>
  </main>
</Layout>